Title: [AFP] Athena 12K Generic Profile V2.2
Desc:
Athena 12K Standard Resin Profile
Version 2.2
Detection Systems:
-Dynamic Wait
-Separation Detection
-Crash Detection
-Resin Level Detection

Heater Control
ShieldBeforeLayer:
G90
SET_PROGRESS_BAR CL=[[LayerNumber]] TL=[[TotalNumberOfLayers]]
MOVE_PLATE Z=[[LayerPosition]] F=600
[[MoveWait 2]]
[[PositionSet [[LayerPosition]]]]
[JS]
if([[_FssEnableDynamicwait]] == 0)output="[[DynamicWaitStart]]";
[/JS]
fss_idle
ShieldAfterLayer:
[JS]if ([[LayerNumber]]==1||[[LayerNumber]]%3==0) output="TRIGGER";[/JS]
[JS]if ([[LayerNumber]]==1||[[LayerNumber]]%5==0) output="M105";[/JS]
[[MoveCounterSet 0]]
UVLED_ON PWM=[[_UvPwmValue]]
DWELL P={[[CureTime]]*1000}
[[MoveWait 1]]
UVLED_OFF 
[[GPIOHigh 10]]

[JS]
var nano = nanodlpContext();
var resinlevel = nano["Status"]["ResinLevelMm"];
if( [[_FssEnablePeeldetection]]==0 && [[CurrentPosition]] > resinlevel) output="[[SeparationDetectionStart]]";
[/JS]

[[MoveCounterSet 0]]
G91
MOVE_PLATE_FSS Z=[[ZLiftDistance]] F={120-([[LayerNumber]]<5)*70}
[[PositionChange [[ZLiftDistance]]]]
[[MoveWait 1]]
[[SeparationDetectionStop]]
[JS]if ([[LayerNumber]]==1||[[LayerNumber]]%100==0) output="G4 P2000";[/JS]
[JS]if ([[LayerNumber]]==1||[[LayerNumber]]%100==0) output="[[PressureWrite 1]]";[/JS]
